{
  "id": "adv_love_2411_08_03",
  "title": "Episode 8 Part 3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――大学一年生　二月",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――February‚ First Year of University",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "電話に出る",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 177.0000328696
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan001.m4a",
              "text": "……あ、繋がった\nもしもーし？　久しぶりじゃん\nちゃんと生きてる？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Ah‚ got through!\nHelloo? Long time no see.\nStill alive over there?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 177.3667228057,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 0
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-koh012.m4a",
              "text": "お、お久しぶりです……\n急に電話きて、ビックリしました",
              "translations": {
                "en": "O-oh‚ it’s been a while…\nDidn’t expect a sudden call from you.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 183.2667228057,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan002.m4a",
              "text": "確かに、叶から連絡する理由\nゼロだからね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "True. There’s basically no reason\nfor me to be calling you at all.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 188.466691271,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-koh013.m4a",
              "text": "（それもあるけど……最後の優さんとの\n通話以来、住む世界の違う芸能界の人に\n俺から連絡をとることなんて出来なかった）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "(She’s not wrong… After that\nlast call with Yu-san‚ I couldn’t\nbring myself to reach out to anyone\nfrom the entertainment world.)",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 193.0333579376,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan003.m4a",
              "text": "てか今日、なんで見送り来なかったの？\nそりゃ、堂々と会いに行くのは\n難しかったかもしんないけどさ……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Anyway‚ why didn’t you come to see\nher off today? Sure‚ it might’ve been\nawkward to show up openly‚ but still…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 205.4666821158,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan004.m4a",
              "text": "どこかでひっそり見送るとかは出来たじゃん\nな……なんなら叶も、少しぐらいは協力\nしてやったのに……少しだけねっ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "You could’ve at least watched from\na distance‚ you know? If you’d asked‚\nI might’ve even helped a little…\na little‚ okay!?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 213.9666821158,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-koh014.m4a",
              "text": "え？　……見送り？\n誰のことですか？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Huh? …See her off?\nWho are you talking about?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 223.7333487824,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 227.0831396417
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan005.m4a",
              "text": "……は？　何それ、笑えない冗談\nてか……マジで言ってんの？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…Huh? That’s not funny.\nWait—are you serious right now?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 227.7666770295,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 235.7000246044
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan006.m4a",
              "text": "今日、優が出発する日じゃん\n本格的にミュージカルを学ぶために\n向こうの演劇学校に数年留学するってやつ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Today’s the day Yu left.\nShe’s going abroad to study musical\ntheatre for a few years‚ remember?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 235.7000246044,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "……そう、だったんですね\nでも、すみません\n俺、あれ以来優さんとは連絡取ってなくて",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…I see… I didn’t know.\nSorry‚ I haven’t been in touch with\nYu-san since back then.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 244.8666912711,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan007.m4a",
              "text": "え、嘘でしょ？\n優はあんたとも、たまに連絡してるって……\n……あ～……そういうことか……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "What? No way.\nShe said she still talked to you\nsometimes… Ah… I see how it is now…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 253.5000215526,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 260.6000328696
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 265.266683133
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan008.m4a",
              "text": "優のやつ、外部との連絡や接触を\n全部事務所側にコントロールされてたんだな\nだから、あんな嘘までついて……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "So her agency must’ve been\ncontrolling all her outside contact\nand communication. That’s why\nshe lied about it…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 265.266683133,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "……え\nそ、そんなことってあり得るんですか？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…Huh? C-can something like that\neven happen?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 274.8333497997,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan009.m4a",
              "text": "優にもブランドイメージがあるからね\nまた変な写真撮られて傷物にされたら\nたまったもんじゃないでしょ、事務所的には",
              "translations": {
                "en": "She’s got a brand image to protect‚\nafter all. If she got caught in\nanother photo scandal‚ it’d be\na nightmare for the agency.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 278.8333843863,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan010.m4a",
              "text": "だったら最初から\n身辺のあれこれを徹底管理して\n商品として守ることぐらいはするよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "So yeah‚ they manage every detail of\nher private life from the start—to\nprotect their “product.”",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 287.8000571564,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan011.m4a",
              "text": "……さてはこの留学も本人の意思じゃないな\n炎上が落ち着くまで留学のテイで海外に\n逃がしたのか……ムカつくやり方だなぁ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Guess this “study abroad” thing\nwasn’t her idea either. They just\nsent her overseas until the flames\ndied down… What a disgusting move.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 294.8333640411,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 306.2268557861
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 307.2666892363
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-koh017.m4a",
              "text": "そ、そんな……！　商品……？\nそこまでするんですか、芸能事務所って……\n芸能界、怖い……コワイ……コワイよぉ……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "N-no way… “Product”…?\nAgencies really go that far…?\nThe entertainment world is scary…\nterrifying… so scary…!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 307.2666892363,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan012.m4a",
              "text": "……はぁ……まあ、あれだね\nあんたには本当に同情するわ\nてか、さすがの叶も普通に引いてるし",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…Haah… yeah.\nI really feel for you‚ honestly.\nEven I’m creeped out by this.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 323.0333457306,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan013.m4a",
              "text": "お別れも言えなかったんじゃねぇ……\nしょうがない、一杯付き合うよ\n抱えてるもの、全部吐き出しちゃえば？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "You didn’t even get to say goodbye‚\nhuh… Fine‚ I’ll join you for a drink.\nJust let it all out‚ okay?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 335.1333559031,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-koh018.m4a",
              "text": "小島先輩……ううぅ……\nありがとうございます……\nその友情が、目に染みて……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Kojima-senpai… ugh…\nThank you so much… Your friendship…\nit brings tears to my eyes…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 346.1333986277,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 353.4666585287
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 354.0000795359
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "kan",
              "speakerName": "小島叶",
              "speakerNameEn": "Kana",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-kan014.m4a",
              "text": "ただし！\nあんたの奢りだからね？\n叶～、お寿司がいいなぁ、回らないやつ！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "But! You’re paying‚ got it?\nI want sushi—real sushi‚\nnot the conveyor-belt kind!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 354.0000795359,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-koh019.m4a",
              "text": "……！　そっちから誘っておいて……\n芸能人……こ、怖い……コワイよぉ……！",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…What!? You’re the one who\ninvited me! Celebrities…\ns-so scary… terrifying…!",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 362.0334128692,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "電話に出ない",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "sfx",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 373.7667462026
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 373.7667462026
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-koh020.m4a",
              "text": "（きっと優さんに関する連絡だろう\n着信音を聞いていると出てしまう気がして\n俺はスマホの電源を切った）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "(It was probably about Yu-san again.\nJust hearing the ringtone made me\nwant to answer‚ so I turned off\nmy phone.)",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 373.7667462026,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "sfx",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 382.1200715252
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-koh021.m4a",
              "text": "……もうやめよう\nすべて終わらせて、忘れて……\n目を覚まして、楽になろう",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…That’s enough.\nIt’s time to end this‚ forget it all…\nWake up and move on.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 382.9667746856,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2411_08_03-koh022.m4a",
              "text": "所詮、俺は一般人だ\nたまたま近くに芸能人がいたってだけの\n単なる凡人でしかないんだから",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I’m just an ordinary guy. A plain\nnobody who happened to cross paths\nwith someone from the entertainment\nworld.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 392.3334637318,
              "sfxList": []
            },
